<h2 id="contributing" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#contributing" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Contributing</h2>
<p>Any change to behavior (including bugfixes) must come with a test.</p>
<p>Patches that fail tests or reduce performance will be rejected.</p>
<div class="language-text ext-text line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code># to run tests
npm test

